    "body": "@cmr the lint pass could return a `HashMap<ast::node_id, level>` where each type declaration in the crate is a key of the hash map and the value is the level of the relevant lint at that time. Over time if we needed to give more lint levels to trans then the value could be a struct.\n\nThen you just have to pass the map to trans which can shove it into the CrateContext\n",
